The Linux App Store

Whether you're a user looking for apps or a developer looking to reach more users, Flathub is the best choice for apps on Linux.

Important note: It is recommended to use Raspberry Pi OS 64-bit as newer applications are more likely to be available for that platform only. Graphical installation of Flatpak apps may not be possible with Raspberry Pi OS. To install Flatpak apps visit https://flathub.org/
